code: @Override public boolean equals(final Object obj) {     if (obj == this) {         return true.     }     if (!(obj instanceof ReferenceId)) {         return false.     }     final ReferenceId other = (ReferenceId) obj.     return Objects.equals(id, other.id) && Objects.equals(referenceId, other.referenceId) && Objects.equals(getErrors(), other.getErrors()). }
